Tga '''Warzazat''' (s [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tmaziɣt]] : ⵡⴰⵔⵣⴰⵣⴰⵜ, s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|tɛrabt]] : ورزازات, s [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tfransist]] d tutlayin yaḍn : Ouarzazate) yat tiɣrmt illan ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Dṛɛa-Tafilalt|Dṛɛa-Tafilalt]] ɣ iffus anammas n tmazirt n [[Lmeɣrib|Lmɣrib]]. Ar as ttinin " Taggurt n tanẓruft " acku tqrrb nit i tnẓruft. Tlla tiɣrmt ad gr idrarn n [[Aṭlas mqqurn|Waṭlas mqqurn]] d tanẓruft, ɣayad ast yujjan ad tili s yat tuttuyt ilkmn ar 1151 m i yill. Ar ittini usiḍn lli ittyuskar ɣ usggʷas n 2014 mas tiɣrmt ad zdɣn gis 71,067 umzdaɣ d 15,475 n tawjiwin.<ref>[http://rgphentableaux.hcp.ma/ RGPH 2014 - Site HCP] - Tasmirit tamattayt n usɣiws.</ref>

Tettuysan Warzazat s [[tamallayt]], tga yat tiɣrmt nna d bahra tkkan irumiyn iɣ d uckan s tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]]. Tama nns nit tlla yan iɣrm bahra ittawsan ig akk UNESCO World Heritage Site, Iɣrm ad iga tt iɣrm n [[Ayt Bn Ḥddu]].

Tettawssan tiɣrmt ad ula s studyuwat n laflam lli gis illan. Kigan n laflan mqqurnin n Marikan ula win umaḍal tettuyṣwarn d tettuytmtaln ɣ ammas n tiɣrmt ad zund matalan: ''[[Lawrence of Arabia (film)|Lawrence of Arabia]]'' (1962), ''[[The Man Who Would Be King (film)|The Man Who Would Be King]]'' (1975), ''[[The Living Daylights]]'' (1987), ''[[The Last Temptation of Christ (film)|The Last Temptation of Christ]]'' (1988), ''[[The Mummy (1999 film)|The Mummy]]'' (1999), ''[[Gladiator (2000 film)|Gladiator]]'' (2000), ''[[Kingdom of Heaven (film)|Kingdom of Heaven]]'' (2005), ''[[Kundun]]'' (1997), ''[[Legionnaire (film)|Legionnaire]]'' (1998), ''[[Hanna (film)|Hanna]]'' (2011), ''[[The Hills Have Eyes (2006 film)|The Hills Have Eyes]] (2006)'', and ''[[Salmon Fishing in the Yemen]]'' (2011) ṣwrn-tn d ɣid, ula yat lpartya n lmuslsal bahra ittawsan ad t igan ''[[Game of Thrones]]''.

== Aẓur n yism ==
Ikka-t-inn udɣar lli ɣ tlla Warzazat iga s yism ''Tamɣzezt'' . Amma Warzazat lli igan ism nns ɣila tga yan wawal [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|amaziɣ]] ibḍa s snat tguriwin ad-tn-t igan: ''War''  d ''Zazat,'' s unamk n " Bla n Ṣḍaɛ " zɛma tiɣrmt ad ur gis illi ṣḍaɛ.

ili ma ittinin mas aẓuṛ n ism ad igat '''War Zzallat''' s unamk n ''Walu timukrisin g tmazirt ad ''. Acku taguri '''War''' g tmaziɣt dars anamk n '''ur illi'''.

